<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>CSS Selectors</title>
  <style>
    /* Element selector */
    body {
      font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    /* Class selector */
    .highlight {
      background-color: #fffae6;
      border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    /* ID selector */
    #main-title {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #2980b9;
    }

    /* Descendant selector */
    .container p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Pseudo-class selector */
    a:hover {
      color: #e74c3c;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Grouped selector */
    h2, h3 {
      color: #6c3483;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1 id="main-title">CSS Selectors Demo</h1>

  <div class="highlight">
    <p>This paragraph is highlighted using a <strong>class selector</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <p>This is a paragraph inside a container div. Styled using a <strong>descendant selector</strong>.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Another Section</h2>
  <h3>Subheading</h3>

  <p>Visit the <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_selectors" target="_blank">MDN CSS Selectors</a> page to learn more.</p>

</body>
</html>
